@startuml
title Immutable Object

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Prevent objects from being modified; safer sharing, easier concurrency.

**Use when**: Value objects (Money, DateTime), thread safety, caching keys.

**Key participants**: An immutable class with final fields, no setters, construction via constructor/builder/copy.
endlegend

class Money <<immutable>> {
  -amount : int
  -currency : String
  +Money(amount:int, currency:String)
  +withAmount(amount:int) : Money
  +withCurrency(currency:String) : Money
}

note right of Money
No setters; state set only at construction.
Mutations return NEW instances.
Safe for sharing across threads.
end note
@enduml